  "title": "Project & Technical Sales Engineer - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Position: Project & Technical Sales Engineer</strong></u><br /><br />Salary: $3600 to $7000 + Bonus<br />Working Days: Monday to Friday (9am-6pm)<br />Working Location: Kaki Bukit</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Possess Electrical Engineering educational qualification</li><li>Relevant working experience in Engineering & onboard vessel site services. </li><li>Knowledge of PAGA, CCTV, PABX, Fire Alarm Systems, Fire & Gas systems, Helideck lightings systems, Weather Monitoring systems, Aids to Navigation systems, Instruments, added advantage.</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities & Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Autocad Drawings and project documentation</li><li>Project administration and scheduling</li><li>Technical Sales proposal and clarifications with customers</li><li>Project engineering and design</li><li>Hands-on product integration , troubleshooting, testing, etc. </li><li>Site Services on board vessel (local & overseas)</li></ul><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
